title: Jordan Klepper Heads to the MAGA Frank Rally | Mary J. Blige
itunes:title: Jordan Klepper Heads to the MAGA Frank Rally | Mary J. Blige
description:
Trevor explores the impact of streaming on the music industry, Jordan Klepper attends the MAGA Frank Rally organized by Mike Lindell, and Mary J. Blige discusses "Mary J. Blige's My Life."

Donate at dailyshow.com/TrevorProject to support The Trevor Project in providing suicide prevention, crisis intervention and education, research and advocacy programs for LGBTQ youth.
